title: 10 Minute Full Body Stretch & Mobility [DAILY ROUTINE]
description:
Tap in with us daily for a 10 minute stretch and mobility routine that will help reduce any pain, tension, or soreness. This session can be used as a wam up or cool down to any of your workouts. If you need to sepnd some extra time on any of these movements, pause the video, and pick back up with us when you're ready.
